00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:39,110
When people drink too much,
we can't move them.

841
00:40:39,110 --> 00:40:40,190
-He might vomit.
-Long time no see.

842
00:40:40,190 --> 00:40:41,440
I've been wanting to thank you.

843
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:42,640
I can't drink either.

844
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,000
It's okay.

845
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:44,630
You can't drink.

846
00:40:44,630 --> 00:40:45,800
Sit here and have a chat.

847
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:48,000
Really, it's good 30-year-old liquor.

848
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:50,370
That's enough.

849
00:40:50,710 --> 00:40:52,000
-I can't drink.
-It's fine.

850
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,840
It's alright, we're happy today.

851
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:54,640
That's right.

852
00:40:54,710 --> 00:40:56,230
You've worked hard lately, Wen Wen.

853
00:40:56,230 --> 00:40:57,000
It's my duty.

854
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:59,510
There's a lot of work to do at home too.

855
00:40:59,510 --> 00:41:01,440
See how busy
my brother-in-law is.

856
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:03,670
Come on, let's have a drink.

857
00:41:03,670 --> 00:41:04,550
It's all in the wine.

858
00:41:04,550 --> 00:41:05,010
Cheers.

859
00:41:05,150 --> 00:41:06,630
Thank you, Wen Wen.

860
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:07,960
I'll drink it all.

861
00:41:10,550 --> 00:41:11,280
Drink it all.

862
00:41:11,360 --> 00:41:12,820
It's fine for young folks.

863
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:23,660
Come on, eat, have a dumpling.

864
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:25,210
I made them.

865
00:41:25,670 --> 00:41:26,480
Have a dumpling.

866
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,480
I don't want any.

867
00:41:27,880 --> 00:41:28,400
You won't eat?

868
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:30,730
If you're not eating, then drink. Come on.

869
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:42,370
Luo Qing.

870
00:41:44,630 --> 00:41:45,360
If you ask me,

871
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:47,230
your ability to
handle pressure is so poor.

872
00:41:47,230 --> 00:41:49,400
You might as well
not be the team leader anymore.

873
00:41:49,400 --> 00:41:50,330
What do you mean?

874
00:41:50,710 --> 00:41:52,170
From what I know about you,

875
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:56,060
the plan you've written must be good.

876
00:41:57,710 --> 00:41:58,550
So in my opinion,

877
00:41:58,550 --> 00:42:00,610
you just can't handle pressure well.

878
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:02,860
You lack confidence in yourself.

879
00:42:03,820 --> 00:42:04,530
The institute has given you

880
00:42:04,530 --> 00:42:06,450
a task beyond your capabilities.

881
00:42:07,230 --> 00:42:08,760
How many eyes are watching?

882
00:42:09,070 --> 00:42:10,400
If anything goes wrong,

883
00:42:10,510 --> 00:42:11,960
not only will you fail to lift the roof,

884
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:14,490
but you'll also
smash the ancestors' skulls.

885
00:42:14,670 --> 00:42:16,920
So you toss and turn, hesitating,

886
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:18,380
unable to make a decision.

887
00:42:20,280 --> 00:42:21,740
What are you trying to say?

888
00:42:24,670 --> 00:42:25,460
You know,

889
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,730
we're archaeologists.

890
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:30,580
It's all about academic work.

891
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:31,400
Right?

892
00:42:32,550 --> 00:42:34,610
But being a team leader is different.

893
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:36,880
A team leader has to make decisions.

894
00:42:37,190 --> 00:42:38,920
If you keep hesitating,

895
00:42:39,670 --> 00:42:41,770
your team members will be on edge too.

896
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:44,080
Whether it's Xiaobai

897
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:45,000
or Hou,

898
00:42:45,710 --> 00:42:47,770
they're not just your support group,

899
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:49,520
they're your teammates too.

900
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:52,320
If one project drains you completely,

901
00:42:53,150 --> 00:42:53,950
then I suggest

902
00:42:54,880 --> 00:42:55,810
you might as well

903
00:42:56,190 --> 00:42:58,800
just go back to
the institute and take an office job.

904
00:42:58,800 --> 00:42:59,840
Wouldn't that be much easier?
